{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_69","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated `fails-native-image-run` job failed for `io.netty:netty-common:4.2.1.Final`. Preserved work is available here: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-7609-fails-native-image-run-io.netty-netty-common-4.2.1.Final-1a5baa02\n\nThe failure most likely happened during native-image test execution for the project that automation appears to have reused at `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final`. On the preserved branch, the only tracked changes are adding `graalvmNative.agent` configuration and `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/user-code-filter.json`. The available Gradle result at `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/build/test-results/test/TEST-Gradle#20Test#20Run#20#3atest.xml` ends with `Process 'Gradle Test Executor 1' finished with non-zero exit value 1`. `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/build/test-results/test/binary/output.bin` is empty, `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/build/native/` only contains `agent-output/test`, and no `4.2.1.Final` execution metrics or matching workflow run logs were produced, so the underlying native runtime exception was not captured.\n\nPlease inspect `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/build/test-results/test/TEST-Gradle#20Test#20Run#20#3atest.xml`, `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/build/reports/tests/test/classes/Gradle#20Test#20Run#20#3atest.html`, `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/src/test/java/netty/NettyTests.java`, and `metadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/reachability-metadata.json`.\n\nRecommended manual follow-up:\n- Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.netty:netty-common:4.2.1.Final --stacktrace` locally and capture the first native-image runtime exception or crash log.\n- Check whether `NettyTests.java` for the `4.1.115.Final` metadata version needs additional reachability metadata for the SSL/HTTP/compression path it exercises on `4.2.1.Final`.\n- If the metadata is still valid after reproduction, update the preserved branch with the real fix and then record `4.2.1.Final` in `metadata/io.netty/netty-common/index.json`."}}
